{"tid":2141050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓法院變賣日商資產恐引日反制 韓外交部威脅撕毀軍情協定","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:56:02.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71c5cb71ba4097e194ab77970844f2fbe398d49d","tid":2141050,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:44:25.000Z","msg":"隨著南韓法院因二戰強徵勞工裁定制裁日商，導致日韓兩國不僅外交再度惡化，還頻頻發動貿易戰、經濟制裁，一度鬧到要世界貿易組織（WTO）介入調停；今天（8月4日）南韓外交部再度提起《日韓軍事情報保護協定》（GSOMIA），揚言視日本的反應「隨時都可以廢止」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《韓聯社》報導，南韓外交部發言人金仁澈表示，南韓政府在去年決定暫停廢除GSOMIA時，就已經預設南韓政府可以單方面中止協定效力，並不會事先通知日本，之後也會就日本是否會撤銷「出口限制措施」的進展，決定是否撕毀GSOMIA，而協定規定的每年自動續約一事「不會繼續採用」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249838&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=efb90ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249838&h=b83ced4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249838</a>"},{"pid":"fa41e513322f13ebb8a9b3b444f181e44b8fdece","tid":2141050,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xFwQEGL9MA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxFwQEGL9MA0&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=3d1cd98b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xFwQEGL9MA0</a><br />\n<br />\n想了解多d可以睇e個<br />\n簡單d講  韓狗搞鳩日本直接令三星輸比台積電<br />\n到最後輸既都只會係韓狗  因為美國同日本已經連成一體<br />\n日本憎韓狗  美國憎韓狗  係亞洲  美國只視澳洲日本為盟友<br />\n琴日仲放風要係南韓撤軍添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720408e64ec46ecf308e1ed32b858e1e5dcbb228","tid":2141050,"uid":143230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa41e513322f13ebb8a9b3b444f181e44b8fdece","tid":2141050,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05